  <brief_title>PLACEBO-CONTROLLED SAFETY STUDY OF RITLECITINIB (PF-06651600) IN ADULTS WITH ALOPECIA AREATA</brief_title>
  <acronym>Allegro2a</acronym>
  <official_title>A PHASE 2a, RANDOMIZED, DOUBLE-BLIND, PLACEBO CONTROLLED STUDY INVESTIGATING THE SAFETY OF RITLECITINIB (PF-06651600) IN ADULT PARTICIPANTS WITH ALOPECIA AREATA</official_title>
