    <arm_group_label>Treatment Arm: PF-06651600</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>ritlecitinib 200 milligram (mg) once per day (QD) (four 50 mg tablets) for 4 weeks then ritlecitinib 50 mg tablet QD through month 24. At Month 9, participants assigned to this treatment arm will also receive 3 tablets of placebo for 4 weeks to maintain the blind with the other arm</description>
